column3: “Chem D.O.G is a good strain but it makes you pass tf out”
“Great strain, pungent to smell, amazing taste when smoked through a bong. Be aware!! Will knock you out with proper dosage!”

“THAT TASTE!
I usually couldn't care less about the taste as long as it's potent. But this is a nice little treat. 
For me the high is obviously indica. Gives you a nice relaxing body buzz great for Netflix & chill. 
If you can find this strain pick it up if you need a good night sleep, but make sure you're actually getting this strain.”
“It was exactly what I was looking for muscles finally relaxed lower back pain subsided”
“Great strain, extremly relaxing... But ist pretty strong, so stay carefull with the dosage”

“this Chem is B.O.M.B. Excellent chemie taste, great head buzz, can you say laugh. Nice day time party strain. the finish has some burn out,not bad thou. Check it out, Its a Chem, so you know its funky cold mabudo. check n it out in Easy Mesa”
“Definitely an Indica. Really relaxed me though.”

“After getting two 8ths im...convinced it's some really good stuff,I must say rite off the bk you taste this spice/kush taste very nice,I describe this in one word heavy,especially leaning towards the evening,definitely will RELAX you into sleep”"

“this Chem is B.O.M.B. Excellent chemie taste, great head buzz, can you say laugh. Nice day time party strain. the finish has some burn out,not bad thou. Check it out, Its a Chem, so you know its funky cold mabudo. check n it out in Easy Mesa”
“Smoked so much but honestly didn’t really feel anything. Felt like I was smoking a mid sour but I did feel a little relaxed and smooth feeling”
“Not a bad strain but you come down from it really quick”

“Couch lock 
Gives you a relaxed calm feeling for naps”
“really relaxing but also makes me happy and talk alot 😇”
